            <bug_when>2009-08-21 11:35:21 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>This is something I have written (quickly) and would like to see as part of the framework. The idea is when a keypress event occurs on a password field, check that the case is lower and shift is not down, or the case is upper and shift is down. If not then the user must have the capslock on.
Would possibly need a property to enable/disable. perhaps on by default but themable?</thetext>
